videoRender.networkError: A network error caused the media download to fail part-way
videoRender.formatError: The media could not be loaded, either because the server or network failed or because the format is not supported
videoRender.corruptionOrSupportError: The media playback was aborted due to a corruption problem or because the media used features your browser did not support
videoRender.sourceError: No compatible source was found for this media
videoRender.encryptionError: The media is encrypted and we do not have the keys to decrypt it
